name: Rocket Boost Alpha 0.5
description:
I'm trying to learn to make a game!

Space to thrust. A and D to turn. 

This is the second playable levels of Rocket Boost (working name) There are 25 levels in total. 

This project is going on hold while I take the next steps in the course. You can see more about that here: 

Music by Natalie Turner: https://twitter.com/NattyWW

Vocals by D1DLC: https://www.youtube.com/d1dlc

Currently working though Complete C# Unity Developer 3D: Learn to Code Making Games by GameDevTV (https://www.gamedev.tv/), via Udemy.
